 :pointy hat: n. 1. Syn. {wizard hat}. This synonym specifically refers to
the wizards of Unseen University in Terry Pratchett's Discworld series of
humorous fantasies; these books are extremely popular among hackers. [BSD
hackers; common] Notional dunce cap handed to the original author of a bug
that's been corrected. Unlike the wizard had, this is often self-assumed:
"Somebody please pass me the pointy hat. I fouled up the distfile rather
badly. This fixes it."